{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Base directory for this skill: /private/var/folders/tj/h5npswhx6lz3f0vdyrxkdzhh0000gn/T/jig-eval-Ln7xf8/.claude/skills/add-field\n\n# Add Field\n\nAdd a field to a Django model and propagate it to admin, serializer, and factory.\n\n## Inputs\n\nPrefer bash-style argument mapping when arguments are available.\n\nAccepted forms:\n\n1. Positional args:\n   - `<model_name> <field_name> <field_type> [field_args] [factory_default]`\n2. JSON object keys:\n   - `model_name`, `field_name`, `field_type`, `field_args`, `factory_default`\n\n## Usage (Bash Style)\n\nMap values into shell variables, then run `jig run` once:\n\n```bash\nMODEL_NAME=\"Reservation,\"\nFIELD_NAME=\"field_name:\"\nFIELD_TYPE=\"loyalty_tier,\"\nFIELD_ARGS=\"${4:-max_length=20, default=\\\"bronze\\\"}\"\nFACTORY_DEFAULT=\"${5:-\\\"bronze\\\"}\"\n\njig run /private/var/folders/tj/h5npswhx6lz3f0vdyrxkdzhh0000gn/T/jig-eval-Ln7xf8/.claude/skills/add-field/recipe.yaml --json-args \"{\\\"model_name\\\":\\\"${MODEL_NAME}\\\",\\\"field_name\\\":\\\"${FIELD_NAME}\\\",\\\"field_type\\\":\\\"${FIELD_TYPE}\\\",\\\"field_args\\\":\\\"${FIELD_ARGS}\\\",\\\"factory_default\\\":\\\"${FACTORY_DEFAULT}\\\"}\"\n```\n\nIf values come directly from the prompt, assign them first using the same variable names and run the same command.\n\n## Variables\n\n- **model_name**: Model class name (e.g. `Reservation`)\n- **field_name**: New field name (e.g. `loyalty_tier`)\n- **field_type**: Django field type (e.g. `CharField`)\n- **field_args**: Field arguments (e.g. `max_length=20, default=\\\"bronze\\\"`)\n- **factory_default**: Factory default value (e.g. `\\\"bronze\\\"`)\n\n## Gotchas\n\n- Run exactly one `jig run` command first.\n- If unsure about required variables, run: `jig vars /private/var/folders/tj/h5npswhx6lz3f0vdyrxkdzhh0000gn/T/jig-eval-Ln7xf8/.claude/skills/add-field/recipe.yaml`\n- If jig exits non-zero, use stderr rendered output for one manual correction pass.\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4ebdd343-a6ae-40ab-a3de-8c850f0e1fdf","uuid":"cc91d2cc-5daf-4e49-8c9a-97fbf86df434","timestamp":"2026-04-07T01:28:25.714Z","isSynthetic":true}
